{id global-option-units, h2 [Global Option Units]}
Global option units are units with "global" option. A valid global option unit should be at the beginning of a line of stdn.
[]
'Multiple global option units are supported. In global option units, the value of options like *src and *href can be a urls file.'
[]
Each global option unit will be compiled to an empty div.
[]
{global, level 2, test []}
{two [
    {display [Source]}
    {display [Result]}
    {lang stdn, code [
        '{global, level 2, test []}'
        '{id e1, orbit test, equation [{display, \'\int_0^\infty e^{-x^2}dx=\frac{\sqrt\pi}2\'}]}'
    ]}
    {id e1, orbit test, equation [{display, '\int_0^\infty e^{-x^2}dx=\frac{\sqrt\pi}2'}]}
]}
